data.description: This newly listed single-family home features a spacious open floor plan with high ceilings, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The property includes a versatile loft, suitable for various uses, and a covered patio and porch for outdoor activities. For those seeking a comfortable and stylish home, this property offers a great opportunity. Contact us for a closer look.
